Legal Counsel,(IP Focused) Strategic Investment Firm, Abu Dhabi
Legal Counsel,(IP Focused) Strategic Investment Firm, Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This is an exciting new role with a government linked strategic investment firm in Abu Dhabi.
The ideal candidate will have a good generalist background handling all in-house legal matters but due to the nature of the company someone with IP experience would be preferred.
Candidates will be able to advise across an array of hard and soft contentious IP matters, including patent litigation, trade marks, passing off, design rights, and copyright.
If you have the necessary skills and experience, please send your CV to:
Richard McLerie in the JLegal UAE office in Dubai.
